</li><li>Escape HTML special characters when printing failed callback creation.
</li><li>Add <a class='wikilink' href='http://sli.ics.uci.edu/PmWiki/Functions#pmcrypt'>pmcrypt()</a> for PHP 5.6 compatibility.
